{"title":"Handsontable-plugin-MergeCells","uid":"7bd034d8c0c4eb1cebe9149a16242bb1","slug":"Handsontable-plugin-MergeCells","date":"2022-04-15T06:27:39.000Z","updated":"2022-11-12T13:13:00.166Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Handsontable-plugin-MergeCells.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://h2.ioliu.cn/bing/QingMingHuangShan_ZH-CN12993895964_1920x1080.jpg?imageslim","content":"<h2 id=\"描述\"><a href=\"#描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"描述\"></a>描述</h2><hr>\n<p>插件，允许合并表格中的单元格(使用初始配置、API或上下文菜单)。</p>\n<h3 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#选项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"选项\"></a>选项</h3><hr>\n<h4 id=\"mergeCells\"><a href=\"#mergeCells\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"mergeCells\"></a>mergeCells</h4><p><code>boolean</code>|<code>Array&lt;object&gt;</code></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">setting</th>\n<th align=\"center\">描述</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>true</code></td>\n<td align=\"center\">开启<code>MergeCells</code>插件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>false</code></td>\n<td align=\"center\">关闭<code>MergeCells</code>插件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>An array of objects</code></td>\n<td align=\"center\">- 开启插件    - 初始化时合并指定单元格</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>若要在Handsontable初始化时合并特定单元格，请将mergeCells选项设置为一个对象数组</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>prop</th>\n<th>desc</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>row</td>\n<td>合并开始行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>col</td>\n<td>合并开始列</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>rowspan</td>\n<td>合并行单元格数量</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>colspan</td>\n<td>合并列单元格数量</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3 id=\"Methods\"><a href=\"#Methods\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Methods\"></a>Methods</h3><h4 id=\"clearCollections\"><a href=\"#clearCollections\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"clearCollections\"></a>clearCollections</h4><p><em>clearCollections()</em></p>\n<p>清除合并单元格效果</p>\n<h4 id=\"disablePlugin\"><a href=\"#disablePlugin\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"disablePlugin\"></a>disablePlugin</h4><p><em>disablePlugin()</em></p>\n<p>禁用单元格合并</p>\n<h4 id=\"enablePlugin\"><a href=\"#enablePlugin\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"enablePlugin\"></a>enablePlugin</h4><p><em>enablePlugin()</em></p>\n<p>启用单元格合并</p>\n<h4 id=\"isEnabled\"><a href=\"#isEnabled\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"isEnabled\"></a>isEnabled</h4><p><em>isEnabled()</em></p>\n<p>检查插件是否启用。此方法在<code>Hooks#beforeInit</code> hook中执行，如果返回true，则调用<code>MergeCells#enablePlugin</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"merge\"><a href=\"#merge\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"merge\"></a>merge</h4><p><em>merge(startRow, startColumn, endRow, endColumn)</em></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Param</th>\n<th>Type</th>\n<th>Desc</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>startRow</td>\n<td>num</td>\n<td>开始行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>startColumn</td>\n<td>num</td>\n<td>开始列</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>endRow</td>\n<td>num</td>\n<td>结束行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>endColumn</td>\n<td>num</td>\n<td>结束列</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>Emits: <code>Hooks#event:beforeMergeCells</code>, <code>Hooks#event:afterMergeCells</code></p>\n<p>合并指定的单元格</p>\n<h4 id=\"mergeSelection\"><a href=\"#mergeSelection\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"mergeSelection\"></a>mergeSelection</h4><p><em>mergeSelection([cellRange])</em></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Param</th>\n<th>Type</th>\n<th>Desc</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>[cellRange]</td>\n<td>CellRange</td>\n<td>选择单元格范围</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>合并作为单元格区域提供的选定内容</p>\n<h4 id=\"unmerge\"><a href=\"#unmerge\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"unmerge\"></a>unmerge</h4><p><em>unmerge(startRow, startColumn, endRow, endColumn)</em></p>\n<p>Emits: <code>Hooks#event:beforeUnmergeCells</code>, <code>Hooks#event:afterUnmergeCells</code></p>\n<p>取消合并的单元格,参数同<code>merge</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"unmergeSelection\"><a href=\"#unmergeSelection\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"unmergeSelection\"></a>unmergeSelection</h4><p><em>unmergeSelection([cellRange])</em></p>\n<p>取消合并作为单元格区域提供的选定内容。参数同<code>mergeSelection</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"updatePlugin\"><a href=\"#updatePlugin\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"updatePlugin\"></a>updatePlugin</h4><p><em>updatePlugin()</em></p>\n<p>更新插件状态</p>\n","text":"描述 插件，允许合并表格中的单元格(使用初始配置、API或上下文菜单)。 选项 mergeCellsboolean|Array&lt;object&gt; setting 描述 true 开启MergeCells插件 false 关闭MergeCells插件 An array o...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Handsontable","slug":"Handsontable","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Handsontable.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">描述</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">选项</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#mergeCells\"><span class=\"toc-text\">mergeCells</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Methods\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Methods</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#clearCollections\"><span class=\"toc-text\">clearCollections</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#disablePlugin\"><span class=\"toc-text\">disablePlugin</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#enablePlugin\"><span class=\"toc-text\">enablePlugin</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#isEnabled\"><span class=\"toc-text\">isEnabled</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#merge\"><span class=\"toc-text\">merge</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#mergeSelection\"><span class=\"toc-text\">mergeSelection</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#unmerge\"><span class=\"toc-text\">unmerge</span